%F A183060 a(n) = n + (A147562(n) - 1)/2, n >= 1.
%F A183060 a(n) = n + 2*A151920(n-2), n >= 2.
%F A183060 a(2^n) = A076024(n+1). - _Nathaniel Johnston_, Mar 14 2011
